### ============================================================
### GENERAL — Public & User endpoints
### ============================================================

### [1] Public hello — không cần token
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/hello

### [2] Xem profile user (yêu cầu ROLE_USER hoặc ROLE_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [3] Admin secret (yêu cầu ROLE_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/secret
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### [4] Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
